Pressure Cooker: Chef vs. Chef - Season 1, Episode 4




Alex Guarnaschelli vs. DJ BBQ

Host Anne-Marie Withenshaw and guest star Alex Guarnaschelli keep things hot by lending their culinary prowess to home cooks Paul Moyer and Carolyn Lum in a head-to-head battle. Anne-Marie also welcomes Food Tube personality DJ BBQ who spurs on home cooks JD Mowat and Kyla Turner in a roller coaster final round and an unexpected decision from tasting expert Giles Coren.




Original Air Date: 14-Feb-2015
